name: Projects Portfolio - Progress Report
query:
select 

name as "Code",
project_name "Project Name",
cost_center as "Profit Center",
percent_complete as "Percent Complete",
expected_start_date as "Expected Start",
expected_end_date as "Expected End",
actual_start_date as "Actual Start",
actual_end_date as "Last Activity Logged",
sales_order as "Order Reference",
total_sales_amount as "Order Value",
estimated_costing as "Estimated Cost",
actual_time as "Hours Spent",
status as "Status"





 from tabProject
 
 where project_type = 'External' and is_active = 'Yes'
